{"tid":1392004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[真相一定要大白] 唔搞清楚呢啲問題，我地等於背叛咗義士","createTime":"2019-07-31T15:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T15:21:49.000Z","uid":198822,"like":36,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"eedfb086876b61bb94a0868dc3e8f47623411008","tid":1392004,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:12:52.000Z","msg":"事緣有個po講緊612基金運作<br />\n入邊啲人講咩<span style=\"color: red;\">第一堂20萬，義務律師，綁死民陣律師</span>呢啲概念<br />\n好多巴絲，包括我都唔係好明白<br />\n有冇熟法律嘅人士/接觸過民陣612基金&amp;星火基金嘅巴打，入嚟解答吓以下問題：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 第一次上court有咩要做？正常收費幾多？<br />\n2. 如果民陣612基金畀二十萬搞呢一次上court，係咪正常價？<br />\n3. 係之後幾次上庭嘅場合，義務律師團隊（不論民陣星火）收幾多錢？根據往例，佢地收嘅錢係咪正常水平？<br />\n4. 有巴打話612基金令義士只能搵民陣義務律師，係咪屬實？點解唔可以轉律師？<br />\n5. 612基金/星火基金事前有冇同義士講過佢地唔可以/可以轉律師？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我唔係熱狗，唔係大台撚。唔好同我講個基金幫到人就得，呢個係錢嘅問題，係香港好多同路人嘅心血；我希望香港人同連登仔可以知道盤數點樣運作，冇咩藉口可以唔公開盤數。亦唔好用hocc/吳靄儀係擔保人呢個理由說服我，呢場運動成功係因為拋棄對名人嘅盲從崇拜。基金如果成效偏低，我有理由相信呢啲基金私吞香港人嘅心血，背叛義士，用人血饅頭自肥。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"47204bcdd875e9f4e669525773ced48e03830a5b","tid":1392004,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:13:18.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DErY1NGl2p_M&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGHWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=407d53bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGHWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=1050e377\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！時代革命！<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong! <br />\nThe Revolution Of Our Times! </span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>五大訴求</strong></span></span></ins><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>Hongkongers 5 Demands:</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n1. Full Withdrawal of the Extradition Bill<br />\n2. Retraction of the Characterisation of the Protestas a Riot<br />\n3. Release all Arrested Protesters<br />\n4. Accountability for Police and Yuen Long White Shirts Brutality<br />\n5. Implement Dual Universal Suffrage<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Rcba2Hh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcba2Hh.png&h=a61a5d44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/fm6yf2o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffm6yf2o.jpg&h=67e4b0d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時間無多，政府拖字訣，想我地自亂陣腳，行動規模必須升級</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca030d4dc2c3198b03a1ebcff7cbacee10bcdc4","tid":1392004,"uid":135445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:13:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e8d3ad214cc0d6b37465b972721b079031386c92","tid":1392004,"uid":188437,"like":4,"dislike":15,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:14:25.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能<br />\n負皮,上一頁"},{"pid":"16a3ad32472ed89303d793191568e558a0c8dec2","tid":1392004,"uid":212119,"like":0,"dis